name: "Mad Dino Zombie" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Crayon and felt pen on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and color.] After a meteorite crashes into a shale bed, the strange, glowing elements saturated a fossilized dinosaur skeleton...and Mad Dino Zombie was born...again!  ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) (with help from my granddaughter, Felicity Echo Hanson)
